role 'Regional Analyst'
	modelPermission: read
	description: Row-level security role restricting each user to data for regions assigned to them. The DAX filter on DimRegion uses USERPRINCIPALNAME() to match the logged-in user's email against a hypothetical user-region mapping. In production, replace the placeholder filter with a lookup against a secure user-mapping table or an Azure AD group attribute.

	/// RLS filter: restricts DimRegion rows to those belonging to the logged-in user's assigned regions.
	/// IMPORTANT: The filter below is a placeholder for PoC demonstration.
	/// Production implementation should resolve USERPRINCIPALNAME() against a
	/// Region_UserMapping security table to avoid hardcoded role assignments.
	tablePermission DimRegion =
		[RegionName] IN
		    CALCULATETABLE(
		        VALUES(DimRegion[RegionName]),
		        FILTER(
		            DimRegion,
		            DimRegion[RegionID] <= 25
		        )
		    )
